# Next.js Web App Patterns

## Next.js 15 Structure
- Use App Router (not Pages Router)
- Follow layout structure in [apps/web/src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/app/layout.tsx)
- Use server and client components appropriately

## Component Patterns
- Use shadcn/ui components from [apps/web/src/components/ui/](mdc:apps/web/src/components/ui/)
- Follow form patterns from [apps/web/src/components/sign-in-form.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/components/sign-in-form.tsx)
- Use Tailwind CSS v4 for styling

## Authentication
- Use Better Auth for web authentication
- Follow auth client setup in [apps/web/src/lib/auth-client.ts](mdc:apps/web/src/lib/auth-client.ts)
- Use proper redirect handling for protected routes

## tRPC Integration
- Use tRPC with TanStack React Query
- Follow setup in [apps/web/src/utils/trpc.ts](mdc:apps/web/src/utils/trpc.ts)
- Use providers pattern from [apps/web/src/components/providers.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/components/providers.tsx)

## File Organization
- App routes in `src/app/` directory
- Components in `src/components/`
- Utilities in `src/lib/` or `src/utils/`
- UI components in `src/components/ui/`

## Styling
- Use Tailwind CSS v4
- Use shadcn/ui component library
- Follow theme provider setup in [apps/web/src/components/theme-provider.tsx](mdc:apps/web/src/components/theme-provider.tsx)
